License scope
-------------

Per LGPL v3 section 5 (Conveying Modified Source Versions), this file is
distributed under the same LGPL-3.0 terms as the upstream source.

**Verbatim copy**: this CoursIA data file is byte-for-byte identical to
the upstream file at the pinned commit ac33f607 — same content, same
